	   <tr><td colspan=1 id=headerrow>Posted @ Sun, Apr 22nd 4:18 PM 2001</td>
	   <td id=headerrow align=right><span id=notbold>Score</span>: Decent<span id=notbold>[2.66]</span></td></tr>
	   <tr><td colspan=2>Haste items don't stack, never will. Your haste, from multiple items, defaults to the item with the best haste percentage. So, an eyepatch and a cloak of flames, gives you the haste from the cloak of flames because it has the highest haste.<br><br>You can only stack, 1 haste item + 1 haste spell, or 1 haste item + 1 haste song, ONLY. <br><br><br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
	   <tr><td colspan=1 >&nbsp;</td><td align=right valign=bottom>
